Scenarios-1 : If we want to share all Constants across application , we can define it in Interface static varibles .

Scenarios2: If Constants are shared only class specific we can define it in Implementaion class leve.



Example :
Time Related changes :
private static final long CONNECTION_TIMEOUT= SECONDS.toMillis(30);
                                                SECONDS.toMillis(5);
                                                MINUTES.toMillis(10);
                                                MINUTES.toMillis(30);
